281:      *   <li>update desiredRatePerSec in Throttler with logCleanerIoMaxBytesPerSecond, if necessary</li>
282:      *   <li>stop current log cleaners and create new ones.</li>
283:      * </ol>
284:      * That ensures that if any of the cleaners had failed, new cleaners are created to match the new config.
285:      *
286:      * @param oldConfig the old log cleaner config
287:      * @param newConfig the new log cleaner config reconfigured
288:      */
289:     @Override
