289:     /**
290:      * Clean the given source log segment into the destination segment using the key=>offset mapping
291:      * provided.
292:      *
293:      * @param topicPartition The topic and partition of the log segment to clean
294:      * @param sourceRecords The dirty log segment
295:      * @param dest The cleaned log segment
296:      * @param map The key=>offset mapping
297:      * @param retainLegacyDeletesAndTxnMarkers Should tombstones (lower than version 2) and markers be retained while cleaning this segment
298:      * @param deleteRetentionMs Defines how long a tombstone should be kept as defined by log configuration
299:      * @param maxLogMessageSize The maximum message size of the corresponding topic
300:      * @param transactionMetadata The state of ongoing transactions which is carried between the cleaning of the grouped segments
