{"content":"300:     /**
301:      * Pause logs cleaning for logs that do not have compaction enabled
302:      * and do not have other deletion or compaction in progress.
303:      * This is to handle potential race between retention and cleaner threads when users
304:      * switch topic configuration between compacted and non-compacted topic.
305:      *
306:      * @return retention logs that have log cleaning successfully paused
307:      */
308:     public List<Map.Entry<TopicPartition, UnifiedLog>> pauseCleaningForNonCompactedPartitions() {
309:         return inLock(lock, () -> {
310:             List<Map.Entry<TopicPartition, UnifiedLog>> deletableLogs = logs.entrySet().stream()
311:                     .filter(entry -> !entry.getValue().config().compact) // pick non-compacted logs
312:                     .filter(entry -> !inProgress.containsKey(entry.getKey())) // skip any logs already in-progress
313:                     .collect(Collectors.toList());
314: 
315:             deletableLogs.forEach(entry -> inProgress.put(entry.getKey(), LogCleaningState.logCleaningPaused(1)));
316: 
317:             return deletableLogs;
318:         });
319:     }
